quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,Ndarahiye k’unyenyeri zikorotse
  53,2,Yuko umuntu wanyu atazimiye canke atakosheje
  53,3,Kandi ntavuga amajambo k’ugushaka kwiwe
  53,4,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose avuga atari uko ari ubutumwa bw’Imana yahawe
  53,5,Yaramwigishije uwufise inguvu nyinshi cane
  53,6,Uwufise ububasha nawe afise uburinganire bukwiye
  53,7,Nawe akaba ari mukirere c’ukubona ibiri hejuru cane
  53,8,Hanyuma aregera n’ukumanuka
  53,9,Guca kuba ubube bw’abo bwo hafi nk’umuheto n ’uwundi biri hafi cane
  53,10,Ica imwereka uyo mukozi wiwe kuvyo yeretswe
  53,11,Umutima ntiwabeshe kuvyo wabonye
  53,12,Mbega muharira nawe kubintu yibonera
  53,13,Yaramubonye ubugira kabiri kw’imanuka ryiwe
  53,14,Kugiti c’amaherezo ryayo kiriho
  53,15,Hafi yaho niho hari uwo murima uzovyagira mwo abantu beranda
  53,16,Mugihe capfuka ico giti nica gipfuse
  53,17,Ijisho naryo ntirya buragijwe canke ntiryarenze akarimbi
  53,18,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tyarabonye\tibintu\tbikuru\tbikuru\tmu\tbimenyetso vy’Umuremyi wiwe"
  53,19,Mbega mwarabonye uwitwa Laata hamwe na Uzzaa
  53,20,Hamwe n’uwitwa Manaata agira gatatu
  53,21,"Mbega\tmwebwe\tmurafise\tibibondo\tvy’abahungu\tnayo\tikaba\tifise ibibondo vy’abakobwa"
  53,22,Iryo n’igabanganywa ry’ubuhemu gusa
  53,23,"Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari amazina gusa mwabahaye mwebwe hamwe n’abavyeyi banyu, Imana rero ntiyamanuye ibimenyetso kuri ivyo kuko badakurikiza atari ivyo bikeka ko nivyo imitima yabo yipfuza, mu vy’ukuri uburokoke bwabashikiye buvuye kumuremyi wabo"
  53,24,Mbega umuntu yoshobora kuronka ico yipfuza cose
  53,25,Ni ivy’Imana gusa haba k’umusi w’imperuka no kw’Isi
  53,26,"Hariho Abamarayika bangahe mw’ijuru, ubusabizi bwabo butazo fasha atari munyuma yaho Imana izotanga uruhusha kuwo yishakiye nuku mwemerera"
  53,27,Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batemera umusi w’imperukara bahamagara Abamarayika ku mazina y’abakenyezi
  53,28,"Nabo ntabumenyi bafise kuri ivyo, kuko bada kurikiza atari ukwikekeranya gusa, mu vy’ukuri ukwikeka ntigufasha ikintu na kimwe imbere y’ukuri"
  53,29,Rero ni wirinde na bamwe baha ibitugu vyabo iki cibutso cacu kandi ntibashaka atari ubuzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi gusa
  53,30,"Aya niyo maherezo yabo mu kumenya kwabo, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’umuntu yazimiye munzira yiwe kandi niyo ifise n’ubumenyi bw’uwarokotse"
  53,31,"Ni vy’Imana ibiri mumajuru hamwe n’ibiri kw’Isi kugira ngo ibahembe abantu babi kumabi yabo yose bagira, n’uguhemba ineza kubantu bagira ineza"
  53,32,"Abatitaho ku bicumuro bikuru bikuru hamwe n’ibikorwa vy’umwanda, dukuye mwo amakosa mato mato, ntankeka Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ikigongwe cinshi, kandi niyo ibazi cane kuva akibarema kuri iy’Isi, no kuva mukiri imbanyi z’abavyeyi banyu, rero ntimusukure imitima yanyu, kuko niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije bw’uwisukuye"
  53,33,Mbega wabonye umwe yahindukira
  53,34,Akaba yatanze bikeyi n’uguca yigumya
  53,35,Mbega arafise ubumenyi bw’ibitaboneka n’ukubibona
  53,36,Canke ntiyabwiwe ibiri mu bitabu vy’’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii)
  53,37,Hamwe n’ibitabu vy’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) yakwijije indagano y’Imana
  53,38,Yuko itakira umutima w’ibicumuro vy’uwundi mutima
  53,39,N’umuntu ntazoronka icarico cose atari kukintu yakoze
  53,40,N’ibikorwa vyiwe yagize bizo bonekana
  53,41,Hanyuma azohembwa impembo yiwe ikwiye
  53,42,Impera n’imperuka n’ugusubira k’Umuremyi wawe
  53,43,Nayo Imana niyo izana ibintu binezereza n’ibitera agahinda
  53,44,Kandi niyo yica n’ukuzura
  53,45,Kandi niyo yaremye ibintu bibiri ikigabo n’ikigore mubintu vyose
  53,46,Mu mbuto z’uruvyaro mugihe zisukiwe mugitereko c’uruvyaro
  53,47,Kandi n’uko hejuru yayo hariho irindi zurwa ry’abantu
  53,48,Kandi kuriyo niyo itanga ibikwiye ni vy’umusesekara
  53,49,Kandi niwe Muremyi w’Inyenyeri yitiriwe Shi’ira
  53,50,Kandi niyo yahoneje Aadi wambere
  53,51,NaThamuda ntihasigaje n’umwe
  53,52,"N’imbere\ty’abo\tabantu\tbo\tkuntumwa\ty’Imana\tNuhu\t(iii)\tnabone barahemukiye imitima yabo gusumba ayandi mabi cane"
  53,53,N’ibisagara vyacuranguwe ikaba ariyo yabi curanguye
  53,54,Irabipfuka ivyapfutswe
  53,55,N’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wawe uyigirira ko amakenga
  53,56,Uyu n’uwutuza mubatuza bakera
  53,57,Icaduka kiri hafi kiregereje
  53,58,Ntawushobora kugikura ho atari Imana yonyene
  53,59,Mbega mutangazwa n’ibi biganiro
  53,60,"N’ugutwenga, kandi mutarira"
  53,61,Murasamaye gusa
  53,62,Rero nimu pfukamire Imana kandi muyisenge